---
// The format that makes it possible -- TDN showcase with a syntax-highlighted sample.
---

<section class="section section--tdn">
  <div class="container">
    <p class="eyebrow">the format that makes it possible</p>
    <h2 class="section__title">meet TDN.</h2>

    <p class="lede">
      TDN exports any TouchDesigner network as a single human-readable YAML file &mdash; operators, parameters, connections, layout, annotations, DAT content &mdash; all of it, in text. Every change becomes a clean diff. Every version is a file your AI agent can read, your team can review, and git can meaningfully compare.
    </p>

    <div class="tdn__grid">
      <pre class="code" aria-label="Sample TDN file"><code><span class="c-k">format</span><span class="c-p">:</span> <span class="c-s">tdn</span>
<span class="c-k">version</span><span class="c-p">:</span> <span class="c-s">'2.0'</span>
<span class="c-k">build</span><span class="c-p">:</span> <span class="c-n">8</span>
<span class="c-k">generator</span><span class="c-p">:</span> <span class="c-s">Embody/6.0.16</span>
<span class="c-k">td_build</span><span class="c-p">:</span> <span class="c-s">099.2025.32820</span>
<span class="c-k">exported_at</span><span class="c-p">:</span> <span class="c-s">'2026-04-10T08:15:00Z'</span>
<span class="c-k">network_path</span><span class="c-p">:</span> <span class="c-s">/project1</span>
<span class="c-k">type</span><span class="c-p">:</span> <span class="c-s">containerCOMP</span>
<span class="c-k">options</span><span class="c-p">:</span>
  <span class="c-k">include_dat_content</span><span class="c-p">:</span> <span class="c-n">true</span>
<span class="c-k">operators</span><span class="c-p">:</span>
<span class="c-p">-</span> <span class="c-k">name</span><span class="c-p">:</span> <span class="c-s">noise1</span>
  <span class="c-k">type</span><span class="c-p">:</span> <span class="c-s">noiseTOP</span>
  <span class="c-k">parameters</span><span class="c-p">:</span>
    <span class="c-k">amp</span><span class="c-p">:</span> <span class="c-n">0.8</span>
    <span class="c-k">period</span><span class="c-p">:</span> <span class="c-s">=absTime.frame * 0.1</span>
  <span class="c-k">flags</span><span class="c-p">:</span>
  <span class="c-p">-</span> <span class="c-s">viewer</span>
<span class="c-p">-</span> <span class="c-k">name</span><span class="c-p">:</span> <span class="c-s">level1</span>
  <span class="c-k">type</span><span class="c-p">:</span> <span class="c-s">levelTOP</span>
  <span class="c-k">parameters</span><span class="c-p">:</span>
    <span class="c-k">opacity</span><span class="c-p">:</span> <span class="c-s">~op('ctrl').par.Fade</span>
  <span class="c-k">flags</span><span class="c-p">:</span>
  <span class="c-p">-</span> <span class="c-s">display</span>
  <span class="c-p">-</span> <span class="c-s">render</span>
  <span class="c-k">position</span><span class="c-p">:</span> <span class="c-p">[</span><span class="c-n">400</span><span class="c-p">,</span> <span class="c-n">0</span><span class="c-p">]</span>
  <span class="c-k">inputs</span><span class="c-p">:</span>
  <span class="c-p">-</span> <span class="c-s">noise1</span>
<span class="c-k">annotations</span><span class="c-p">:</span>
<span class="c-p">-</span> <span class="c-k">name</span><span class="c-p">:</span> <span class="c-s">annot1</span>
  <span class="c-k">mode</span><span class="c-p">:</span> <span class="c-s">annotate</span>
  <span class="c-k">title</span><span class="c-p">:</span> <span class="c-s">noise pipeline</span>
  <span class="c-k">position</span><span class="c-p">:</span> <span class="c-p">[</span><span class="c-n">-100</span><span class="c-p">,</span> <span class="c-n">-200</span><span class="c-p">]</span>
  <span class="c-k">size</span><span class="c-p">:</span> <span class="c-p">[</span><span class="c-n">700</span><span class="c-p">,</span> <span class="c-n">400</span><span class="c-p">]</span></code></pre>

      <ul class="tdn__bullets">
        <li><strong>Non-default-only</strong> &mdash; only what you actually changed gets written.</li>
        <li><strong>Type defaults hoisted</strong> &mdash; shared properties dedupe across operators.</li>
        <li><strong>Expression shorthand</strong> &mdash; <code>=absTime.frame * 0.1</code> instead of verbose wrapper objects.</li>
        <li><strong>Round-trip safe</strong> &mdash; export &rarr; edit &rarr; import yields the same network.</li>
        <li><strong>The substrate</strong> for the entire workflow &mdash; forward velocity AND lateral velocity depend on it.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <p class="tdn__callout"><span class="tdn__callout-lead">Diffable.</span> Any text tool, any diff viewer, any AI agent can read it.</p>

    <p class="tdn__closer">
      TDN is what makes the rest of this possible.
    </p>

    <p class="tdn__link">
      <a href="https://dylanroscover.github.io/Embody/tdn/specification/">Read the full TDN specification <span aria-hidden="true">&rarr;</span></a>
    </p>
  </div>
</section>
